metadata.name: Broke Boi
metadata.description:
Down bad!! Spent my MAYC profits on rugs. Flipped my way back to a job. Still trying to party with you! 

Holders will be able to redeem a complementary music service by yours truly. Got a song you need mixed? Want to master it? Maybe it needs some guitar or drums? I gotchu, fam! 

Even if you’re not a musician, I bet you know one who’d absolutely love the gift of a music service. Especially, since studio time starts at $45-$75 per hour. 

Now Available: Lessons in Protools and Mixing! 
That's right. To turn up even more, I want to turn you into a ProTools ninja. Additionally, we can go over basic mixing concepts. Just schedule a time and LFG!!

Head to www.sayten89.com - where you’ll find examples of my work, and can sign up to a mailing list so we can stay in touch!
